---
import LayoutBare from "../layouts/LayoutBare.astro";
import "../styles/v3-sunset.css";
---

<LayoutBare
  title="Privacy Policy · Jetski Lefkada Rentals"
  description="Privacy policy and data protection information for Jetski Lefkada Rentals."
>
  <div class="v3 min-h-screen py-32 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <a href="/" class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] flex items-center gap-2 mb-12" style="color: var(--v3-flame-500);">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
        Back
      </a>

      <div class="v3-eyebrow mb-6"><span>Legal</span></div>
      <h1 class="v3-display text-5xl lg:text-7xl mb-4"><em>Privacy Policy.</em></h1>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-16" style="color: var(--v3-peach-300);">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,230,212,0.8);">
        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">1. Data Controller</h2>
          <p>Jetski Lefkada Rentals, Nidri Marina, Lefkada 31100, Greece.<br />
          Contact: <a href="mailto:info@jetski-lefkada-rentals.com" style="color: var(--v3-flame-500);">info@jetski-lefkada-rentals.com</a></p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">2. Data We Collect</h2>
          <p>When you use our booking inquiry form, we collect: name, phone number, email (if provided), desired date, and any message you write. This data is used solely to process your booking inquiry and communicate with you about your reservation.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">3. Legal Basis</h2>
          <p>Data processing is based on Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR (performance of a contract / pre-contractual measures) and Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in responding to inquiries).</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">4. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>Booking inquiry data is retained for the duration necessary to process your request and for up to 3 years for legal compliance purposes. Payment data is processed by our payment providers and not stored by us.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>Our website uses: Unsplash (images, no personal data), Mixkit (video, no personal data), Formsubmit.co (form processing — see their privacy policy). We do not use tracking cookies or analytics.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">6. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
          <p>You have the right to access, rectify, erase, restrict processing of, and port your personal data. You also have the right to object to processing and to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@jetski-lefkada-rentals.com" style="color: var(--v3-flame-500);">info@jetski-lefkada-rentals.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">7. Cookies</h2>
          <p>This website does not use cookies for tracking or analytics purposes. No cookie consent banner is required.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LayoutBare>
